headline: XLCS Partners advises The Total Garage Store on its investment by U.S. Dock & Door
summary: XLCS Partners, Inc., a leading middle-market investment bank, is pleased to announce it served as the exclusive advisor to The Total Garage Store (TGS) on its investment by U.S. Dock & Door (USDD), a portfolio company of Soundcore Capital Partners.
